data.title: Garcia for WA U.S. Senate
data.meta_description: Putting People First: Health, Leadership, Unity. Dr. Garcia has announced his candidacy for the WA U.S. Senate in the upcoming 2024 election.
data.text:
I am a Doctor and have worked in and managed Emergency Rooms for 25 years. I am proud to be able to help people at their most vulnerable and in moments of fear and uncertainty.

Through a career in medicine, I have had the privilege of working with people from all walks of life.

While I’m not a politician by trade and did not seek out a life in politics, it’s clear the interests of the people of Washington are not being heard in D.C.

With your help, I believe we can become united by one common goal: to restore the safe and prosperous lives of our WA families.
